<li><a href="../E._O._Wilson" title="E. O. Wilson">Wilson, Edward O.</a> <i>Naturalist</i>. Island Press, 1994.</li>
<li><a href="Carl_Zimmer" title="Carl Zimmer">Zimmer, Carl</a>. <i>Evolution: the triumph of an idea</i>. HarperCollins: New York, 2001. <a href="Special_BookSources/0061138401" class="internal mw-magiclink-isbn">ISBN 0-06-113840-1</a></li>
</ul>
</div>
